000610******************************************************************        
000621*                                                                *        
000622* THIS PROGRAM WILL USE THE EXTRACT FILE CREATED BY PCKUT987 OF  *        
000630* OLD IT FROM PCT_TRN_CLSN_DTL THAT HAVE NOT PURGED FORM THE     *        
000640* TABLES.  WILL UPDATE PCT_TRN_CLSN_BAL IT QUANTITIES            *        
000651*                                                                *        
000652* THIS WAS COPIED FROM PKCUP992 BY RON KRIER ON 10/10/2017.      *        
000653* ADDED AN OUTPUT FILE TO THIS PROGRAM TO CREATE A FILE THAT     *        
000654* WILL LIST THE SKU, STORE, BEFORE QUANTITY, AFTER QUANTITY      *        
000655* AND NET CHANGE QUANTITY.                                       *        
000657*                                                                *        
000660******************************************************************        
